## 02. HTML template

html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>Hello World</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Welcome to my web page</h1>
    </body>
</html>


## 03. Paragraph



html
<p>This is a text paragraph</p>


## 04. List



üåµ List ‡πÉ‡∏ô `HTML` ‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö

- Unordered List
- Ordered List

html
<ul>
    <li>Hotdog</li>
    <li>Hamburger</li>
    <li>Pizza</li>
</ul>

<ol>
    <li>Hotdog</li>
    <li>Hamburger</li>
    <li>Pizza</li>
</ol>


## 05. Link (anchor tag)

html
<a href="https://www.google.com" target="_blank">Google Website</a>


## 06. Image


html
<img src="image.jpg" alt="alternate text" width="640">


## 07. Video



html
<video width="640" height="480" controls>
    <source src="yourvideo.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>


## 08. Div

html
<div style="background-color: gold;">
		<h1>Welcome to my Web Page</h1>
		<p>HTML is the core language of web development</p>
</div>


html
<div class="first">
    <!-- our first section -->
</div>

<div class="second">
    <!-- our second section -->
</div>

<div class="third">
    <!-- our third section -->
</div>


## 09. Style

html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>Hello World</title>
        <style>
            h1 {
                color: salmon;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Welcome to my webpage</h1>
    </body>
</html>


## 10. Add comment to HTML file

[https://vimeo.com/481178580](https://vimeo.com/481178580)

html
<!-- this is a comment -->
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Hello World</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Welcome to my web page</h1>
    </body>
</html>




html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Hello World</title>
        <!-- This is my comment -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <div>
            <!-- 
            <h1>Welcome to my Web Page</h1>
            <p>HTML is the core language of web development, 
               together with CSS and JS.</p> -->
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2>My favorite food</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Hamburger</li>
                <li>Hotdog</li>
                <li>Pizza</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2>This is my dog</h2>
            <img src="dog.jpg" width="320">
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
